---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout
  title="About – NOÜVE · moi"
  description="The philosophy behind NOÜVE · moi wellness rituals."
>

<!-- HERO -->
<section class="relative w-screen left-1/2 right-1/2 -ml-[50vw] -mr-[50vw] bg-hero-bg py-24 md:py-32 text-center overflow-hidden">

<div class="absolute inset-0 bg-[radial-gradient(circle_at_top,rgba(85,198,183,0.25),transparent_60%)] pointer-events-none"></div>

<div class="relative mx-auto max-w-3xl px-6">

<p class="text-tiffany uppercase tracking-[0.35em] text-xs font-semibold mb-5">
Our Story
</p>

<h1 class="text-5xl md:text-6xl font-heading font-bold mb-8 text-gray-900">
The Philosophy of NOÜVE · moi
</h1>

<p class="text-lg md:text-xl text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
NOÜVE · moi was created from a simple belief — wellness should feel
intentional, refined, and deeply personal.
</p>

</div>

</section>



<!-- BRAND PHILOSOPHY -->
<section class="container mx-auto px-6 py-20 max-w-5xl text-center">

<p class="text-tiffany uppercase tracking-[0.35em] text-xs font-semibold mb-4">
Philosophy
</p>

<h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-heading font-bold mb-10 text-gray-900">
Wellness, Reimagined
</h2>

<div class="space-y-6 text-lg text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">

<p>
In a world of loud marketing and endless supplements, NOÜVE · moi
was designed to be different — thoughtful, intentional, and quietly luxurious.
</p>

<p>
We believe wellness should integrate seamlessly into daily life,
supporting how you feel, how you move through the world,
and how you evolve.
</p>

<p>
Each formula and ritual is chosen not just for effectiveness,
but for how it enhances the experience of caring for yourself.
</p>

</div>

</section>



<!-- FOUNDER SECTION -->
<section class="relative w-screen left-1/2 right-1/2 -ml-[50vw] -mr-[50vw] bg-hero-bg py-20 overflow-hidden">

<div class="mx-auto max-w-6xl px-6">

<div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row items-center gap-16">

<div class="w-full md:w-1/2">

<img
src="https://picsum.photos/900/1100?portrait"
alt="Founder portrait"
class="w-full rounded-3xl shadow-hover object-cover"
/>

</div>

<div class="w-full md:w-1/2 bg-white/70 backdrop-blur-sm rounded-3xl p-10 shadow-soft">

<p class="text-tiffany uppercase tracking-[0.35em] text-xs font-semibold mb-4">
Founder
</p>

<h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-heading font-bold mb-6 text-gray-900">
A Personal Ritual
</h2>

<p class="text-lg text-gray-700 mb-6 leading-relaxed">
NOÜVE · moi began as a personal search for wellness
that felt elevated rather than overwhelming.
</p>

<p class="text-lg text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
Instead of chasing trends, the goal was to create
rituals that support clarity, vitality, and balance —
all while maintaining a sense of beauty and simplicity.
</p>

</div>

</div>

</div>

</section>



<!-- VALUES -->
<section class="container mx-auto px-6 py-20 max-w-6xl text-center">

<p class="text-tiffany uppercase tracking-[0.35em] text-xs font-semibold mb-4">
Our Values
</p>

<h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-heading font-bold mb-14 text-gray-900">
What Guides Us
</h2>

<div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-10 text-left">

<div>
<h3 class="font-heading text-2xl font-bold mb-4">Intentional Formulas</h3>
<p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
Every ingredient is selected with purpose —
balancing effectiveness with long-term wellness.
</p>
</div>

<div>
<h3 class="font-heading text-2xl font-bold mb-4">Modern Rituals</h3>
<p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
Wellness should fit naturally into daily life,
not feel like a complicated routine.
</p>
</div>

<div>
<h3 class="font-heading text-2xl font-bold mb-4">Quiet Luxury</h3>
<p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
From formulation to design,
every detail reflects thoughtful simplicity.
</p>
</div>

</div>

</section>



<!-- CTA -->
<section class="relative w-screen left-1/2 right-1/2 -ml-[50vw] -mr-[50vw] bg-hero-bg py-20 text-center overflow-hidden">

<div class="mx-auto max-w-3xl px-6">

<h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-heading font-bold mb-8 text-gray-900">
Discover the Collection
</h2>

<p class="text-lg text-gray-700 mb-10">
Explore wellness rituals designed for your next era.
</p>

<a
href="/shop"
class="inline-block bg-gray-900 text-white px-10 py-4 rounded-full font-semibold text-lg hover:bg-gray-800 transition shadow-card"
>
Shop Now
</a>

</div>
<div class="w-1/2 h-[2px] bg-gradient-to-r from-transparent via-tiffany to-transparent mx-auto mb-20"></div>


</section>

</BaseLayout>